title: Income by Place of Residence and Gender, Nashville TN, 2000
name: Income by Place of Residence and Gender, Nashville TN, 2000
description: This dataset shows the incomes of residents. The data is part of the Census Transportation Planning Package (CTPP), and is the result of a cooperative effort between various groups including the State Departments of Transportation, U.S. Census Bureau, and the Federal Highway Administration. The data is a special tabulation of responses from households completing the decennial census long form. The data was collected in 2000 and is shown at tract level.

author.source: US Census (Census Transportation Planning Package) CTPP
